===Etymology===
Noun of action from [[tintinnabulate]], from Latin [[tintinnabulum]] "a bell," from [[tintinnare]], a reduplicated form of from [[tinnire]], "to ring, to jingle."

===Noun===
'''tintinnabulation'''
# A tinkling sound, as of a bell or bells.

